## [2026-03-06] - Auth + Chat Resilience + Pipeline Timeout Fix (v0.10.38)

**What we did:** Fixed 5 bugs across auth, chat, pipeline, and UI. Full E2E flow verified (homepage → sign-in → chat → 7-agent pipeline → report). Session 22 comprehensive audit.

