- `GlobalAIAssistant.tsx`: Added `/validator` to DASHBOARD_PREFIXES (two icons stacking on report pages)

### Test Fix
- `ReportV2Layout.test.tsx`: `getByText → getAllByText` for 'Market Size' (multiple matching elements)

