## [2026-03-01] - Validator Pipeline Fixes + Dynamic Suggestion Chips (v0.10.33)

**What we did:** Fixed two validator pipeline bugs (Group C silent failure, competitor URL context) and added AI-generated dynamic suggestion chips to the chat intake. Each follow-up question now generates 2-4 contextual chips via Gemini, replacing static chips with question-specific options founders can tap.

### 035-GCF: Composer Group C Silent Failure Fix

Fixed a bug where `composer.ts` Group C would silently return empty results when the Gemini response failed to parse, causing missing execution/economics data in reports.

