### 036-CUC: Competitor URL Context Fix

Enabled the existing URL Context feature for founder-provided competitor URLs, allowing the CompetitorAgent to read actual competitor websites.

- `supabase/functions/validator-start/competitors.ts` — Wired `url_context_metadata` extraction for competitor analysis
- `supabase/functions/validator-start/config.ts` — Enabled URL context in competitor agent config

### 037-DSC: Dynamic AI Suggestion Chips

Each follow-up question now includes 2-4 AI-generated suggestion chips that are contextual to the question being asked (e.g., "Monthly SaaS subscription" for business model questions).

- `supabase/functions/validator-followup/schema.ts` — Added `suggestions: string[]` to FollowupResponse interface + Gemini JSON schema (`required`, `properties`, 0-4 items, 60 char max)
- `supabase/functions/validator-followup/prompt.ts` — Added "Suggestion Chips" section: 5 rules + 4 question→chip examples
- `supabase/functions/validator-followup/index.ts` — Validate/sanitize suggestions (cap 4, 60 chars, HTML strip, console.warn for non-strings), add to `followup_ready` + `followup_metadata` broadcasts + HTTP response
- `src/hooks/useValidatorFollowup.ts` — Added `suggestions: string[]` to FollowupResult, pass from HTTP response + streaming metadata
- `src/components/validator/chat/ValidatorChat.tsx` — `latestSuggestions` state, set on ask, clear on ready/error/send, pass to input
- `src/components/validator/chat/ValidatorChatInput.tsx` — Dynamic/static chip selection, primary styling for dynamic chips, fallback to static for initial state

