## [2026-02-27] - MVP-01 V3 Types + React Error #31 Fix + Auth Redirect Fix (v0.10.31)

**What we did:** Implemented MVP-01 V3 types foundation for consulting-grade dimension detail pages. Fixed React Error #31 crash where JSONB objects were rendered as React children. Fixed auth redirect flow where `redirectTo` query params broke Supabase URL allowlist matching. Added 32 regression tests across 2 new test files.

### MVP-01: V3 Types Foundation

- `supabase/functions/validator-start/types.ts` — Added `SubScore`, `DimensionDetail`, `AIStrategyAssessment`, `ValidationProofAssessment` interfaces + 9 optional `*_detail` fields on `ValidatorReport` + `ComposerGroupE` interface
- `supabase/functions/validator-start/schemas.ts` — Added `dimensionDetail` JSON schema building block + `DIMENSION_SUB_SCORES` config constant (9 dimensions, 4-5 sub-scores each)
- `src/types/validation-report.ts` — Mirrored backend types + added `ReportDetailsV2` named type (replaces inline `any`) + `V3ReportDetails` extension + `isV3Report()` type guard
- `src/pages/ValidatorReport.tsx` — Replaced inline `details` type with `ReportDetailsV2` import
- `src/components/validator/report/ReportV2Layout.tsx` — Replaced `details: any` with `ReportDetailsV2`
- `src/pages/SharedReport.tsx` + `EmbedReport.tsx` — Replaced `details: any` with `ReportDetailsV2`

### Audit 30: React Error #31 — Report Crash Fix

- Root cause: Global `isV2Report()` boolean gated per-field type checks. Mixed-format JSONB (V1 strings + V2 objects) caused objects to fall through to string rendering paths → "Objects are not valid as React children"
- `ReportV2Layout.tsx` — 7 fixes:
  - Added `safeText()` universal helper: handles string, null, number, boolean, and object → extracts `.action`/`.assumption`/`.title`/`.description` or falls back to `JSON.stringify`
  - Removed `v2 &&` gate from `risks_assumptions` and `next_steps` checks — each field now does per-field type detection
  - Added shape validation before component delegation (`.assumption` for RiskHeatmap, `.action && .timeframe` for NextStepsTimeline)
  - Applied `safeText()` to 6 JSX text-rendering locations (highlights, red_flags, risks fallback, next_steps fallback, overview next_steps, fatalItem)
- `src/test/components/ReportV2Layout.test.tsx` — 6 new regression tests covering mixed-format, missing fields, unknown object shapes

### Audit 31: Auth Redirect Flow Fix

- Root cause: `useAuth.signInWithGoogle()` appended `?next=...` to `redirectTo` URL. Supabase URL matching includes query params → allowlist mismatch → OAuth redirected to site URL (`/`) instead of `/auth/callback`.
- 3 fixes:
  1. `src/hooks/useAuth.tsx` — Removed `?next=` from `redirectTo`. Return path stored in sessionStorage via `setReturnPathOnce()`. Clean callback URL matches Supabase allowlist.
  2. `src/components/marketing/HeroSection.tsx` — Added loading overlay when `pendingIdea` exists but `user` is null (auth hydrating after OAuth). Shows "Completing sign in..." instead of empty textarea.
  3. `src/pages/AuthCallback.tsx` — Added 15s timeout. If auth exchange never fires, redirects to `/login` instead of spinner forever.
- `src/test/auth-redirect-flow.test.ts` — 26 new tests covering authReturnPath utility, redirectTo construction, pendingIdea flow, callback destination logic, full flow simulation (happy path + fallback)

### Verification

- `npm run build` — 0 TS errors
- `npm run test` — **357/357** pass (325 existing + 6 Error #31 + 26 auth flow)
- Lint (modified files) — 0 new errors

