## [2026-02-06] - Prompt 14: AI-Powered Smart Follow-Up Questions

**What we did:** Replaced 7 static follow-up questions with an AI-powered system. After each founder response, Gemini Flash analyzes the conversation, spots gaps across 8 topics, and generates the next best contextual question. When enough context is gathered (4-7 exchanges), it signals "ready to generate." Includes full audit (6 gaps found, 5 fixed, 1 non-issue) and 3 edge function deployments.

### New Edge Function — `validator-followup` (v3)

4 files, Deno runtime, deployed to Supabase:
- `index.ts` — CORS, auth, input sanitization (max 20 msgs, 2000 chars each, strip HTML), Gemini Flash call, 8s timeout, 1 retry
- `gemini.ts` — Copy of `validator-start/gemini.ts` (Deno isolates functions), `maxOutputTokens: 512` (not 8192)
- `prompt.ts` — System prompt with 8-topic checklist: problem > customer > competitors > innovation > uniqueness > demand > research > websites
- `schema.ts` — `FollowupResponse` interface + `followupResponseSchema` for Gemini `responseJsonSchema`

### New Frontend Hook — `useValidatorFollowup`

- `src/hooks/useValidatorFollowup.ts` — Calls `supabase.functions.invoke('validator-followup', { body: { messages } })`
- Returns `{ getNextQuestion, isLoading, error }`

### ValidatorChat.tsx Rewrite

| Removed | Added |
|---------|-------|
| `FOLLOW_UP_QUESTIONS` static array | `useValidatorFollowup` hook |
| `questionIndex` state | `followupInFlight` ref (concurrency guard) |
| `dataKeys` array | `canGenerate` as state (was computed) |
| `extractedData` state | `fallbackIndex` + 3 fallback questions |
| Unused imports (motion, useNavigate, supabase, useToast) | `MIN_EXCHANGES=2`, `MAX_EXCHANGES=7` safety caps |

### Audit Findings (G1-G6)

| ID | Severity | Issue | Fix | Status |
|----|:--------:|-------|-----|:------:|
| G1 | CRITICAL | Race condition — concurrent `askFollowup` calls | `followupInFlight` useRef guard | FIXED |
| G2 | CRITICAL | Input not disabled during AI thinking | Pass `isProcessing \|\| isTyping` to disable input | FIXED |
| G3 | HIGH | 5s timeout too short for cold starts | Increased to 8000ms | FIXED |
| G4 | HIGH | `maxOutputTokens: 8192` wastes cost | Reduced to 512 in gemini.ts copy | FIXED |
| G5 | MEDIUM | CORS `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` not set for prod | Non-issue — Supabase JS client bypasses browser CORS | N/A |
| G6 | MEDIUM | JWT verification state after double deploy | Verified active on v3 deploy | FIXED |

### Files Created

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `supabase/functions/validator-followup/index.ts` | Edge function entry point |
| `supabase/functions/validator-followup/gemini.ts` | Gemini API client (512 token cap) |
| `supabase/functions/validator-followup/prompt.ts` | System prompt + topic checklist |
| `supabase/functions/validator-followup/schema.ts` | Response schema for guaranteed JSON |
