## [2026-02-05] - Pipeline E2E Verified: OAuth Fix, Model Switch, Timeout Tuning

**What we did:** Fixed remaining production blockers (OAuth redirect, JSON parsing, agent timeouts) and verified the full pipeline end-to-end. Pipeline now produces complete 7-section reports with citations, scores, and AI verification. Compared output against IdeaProof competitor.

### OAuth Redirect Fix

| File | Fix | Impact |
|------|-----|--------|
| `src/pages/AuthCallback.tsx` | Check `pendingIdea` in sessionStorage before default redirect | Homepage → Login → OAuth → Validator flow works |
| `src/pages/Login.tsx` | Read `redirect` from URL query params as fallback | HeroSection's `?redirect=/validate` now works |

**Root cause:** HeroSection passes redirect as URL query param (`/login?redirect=/validate&hasIdea=true`), but AuthCallback always redirected to `/dashboard` or `/onboarding`, ignoring pending ideas. Additionally, Supabase Site URL was set to `https://www.startupai.me/**` (wildcards not allowed in Site URL) causing `/**` 404 on production.

### Pipeline Reliability Fixes

| Fix | Before | After | Impact |
|-----|--------|-------|--------|
| extractJSON balanced brace | Greedy regex `\{[\s\S]*\}` captured trailing search grounding text | Depth-counting brace matcher finds first complete JSON object | No more JSON parse errors from Google Search metadata |
| Model switch | Research + Competitors used `gemini-3-pro-preview` | Switched to `gemini-3-flash-preview` | Agents complete in 10-25s instead of timing out at 35s |
| Agent timeouts | All agents 25-35s | Extractor 30s, Research/Competitors/Composer 60s, Scoring 45s, MVP 30s | No more timeout failures |
| Polling timeout | 3 min (`MAX_POLL_MS = 180_000`) | 5 min (`MAX_POLL_MS = 300_000`) | Frontend doesn't give up while pipeline still running |

